author: Staff Report
title: Stankiewicz,Dunne paceMontrosevolleyball
text:
Megan Dunne had 13 kills and 15 blocks and Emily Stankiewicz had five kills, six digs and 18 assists to lead Montrose to a 3-1 win over Western Wayne in a Lackawanna League girls volleyball match Saturday. 
Kylie Robinson added five kills for the Lady Meteors. 
Jess Berger had seven kills for Western Wayne and JeAnna Pavlovich had five kills and 19 assists.
